title: Business as usual at UNSW today (UNSW - The University of New South Wales)
text: ( Source : UNSW - The University of New South Wales ) Staff and students should remain vigilant and alert, but not alarmed as investigations by NSW Police continue into a security threat made against the University . Classes will run as normal.
